data.title: International spies collection : Austin Powers international man of mystery ; Austin Powers : the spy who shagged me ; Austin Powers in Goldmember ; Spies like us
data.meta_description: Austin Powers international man of mystery: Frozen in the 60's, secret agent Austin Powers (Myers) is thawed back into action to once again battle his archenemy Dr. Evil (Myers). With his sexy sidekic
data.text:
Austin Powers international man of mystery originally released in 1997; Austin Powers : the spy who shagged me originally released in 1999; Austin Powers in Goldmember originally released in 2002; Spies like us originally released in 1985

Title from container

Widescreen 2.4:1 (Austin Powers movies) ; Full screen 1.33:1 (Spies like us)

Austin Powers: International Man Of Mystery Includes: commentary by Mike Myers and director Jay Roach; deleted scenes, including 2 alternate endings; theatrical trailer

Austin Powers: The Spy Who Shagged Me special features: commentary by Mike Myers, director Jay Roach and co-Writer Michael McCullers; deleted scenes; behind-the-scenes featurette gallery; Comedy Central Canned Ham The Dr. Evil Story; 4 music videos: Madonna's Beautiful stranger, Lenny Kravitz's American woman, Mel B's (aka Scary Spice) Word up, and Dr. Evil and Mini-Me's Just the two of us; theatrical trailer

Austin Powers In Goldmember special features: Fact Track trivia subtitle track; commentary by Mike Myers and director Jay Roach; deleted/alternate scenes; 4 mini-documentaries; The world Of Austin Powers featurette gallery; 4 music videos: Beyonce Knowles' Work it out, Britney Spears' Boys, Ming Teas's Daddy wasn't there, Dr. Evil and Mini Me's Hard knock life; theatrical trailers
